{"tid":1633511,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"毛澤東：不能每天高潮，要波浪式前進","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T14:26:27.000Z","uid":235257,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7ecae1e1d9c237ad1d370d476315163429a6ba","tid":1633511,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:18:38.000Z","msg":"在毛澤東批評胡喬木的時候，其實已經覺察出大躍進的問題，所以對指標曾提出：「不能每天高潮，要波浪式前進」。陳雲適時地對毛提出1800萬噸難以完成，毛澤東直接說，「那就拉倒！」這表明毛已經著手要調整高指標。想起陳雲以前的反冒進，毛澤東說陳雲「很勇敢，堅持真理也勇敢。真理往往在一個人手裡。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n革命大師都係咁講，義士係咪要日日出動自己諗<br />\n<br />\n#天滅中共<br />\n#全黨死清光<br />\n#五大訴求<br />\n#缺一不可"},{"pid":"0a5ef9d750f0b79d6d2c4be88ba4287ffe0189bc","tid":1633511,"uid":138212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:41:29.000Z","msg":"毛澤東說陳雲「很勇敢，堅持真理也勇敢。真理往往在一個人手裡。」"},{"pid":"90af6949da0d1140c779bb6a4576deab4bfc7cda","tid":1633511,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:42:15.000Z","msg":"搞埋今日，有四日可以抖喎"},{"pid":"2e9613c536406363f42bb94651a3231dac452c77","tid":1633511,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:48:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbaae5ea9dd0071c6cfb10bb8a4f321d33183dbb","tid":1633511,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc37e4ed25d5c63cb21eb2a7ab64de098bb4c9a2","tid":1633511,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a5ef9d750f0b79d6d2c4be88ba4287ffe0189bc","tid":1633511,"uid":138212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:41:29.000Z","msg":"毛澤東說陳雲「很勇敢，堅持真理也勇敢。真理往往在一個人手裡。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:45:15.000Z","msg":"我神雲與天地同在"},{"pid":"11e1daf42034f066fa9b7a45cde3bdbe8aab2439","tid":1633511,"uid":266325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:46:03.000Z","msg":"係時候收收手先啦 和理非出場"},{"pid":"6b6d18bfb48ebc31